      children: "1966 y\u0131l\u0131nda yap\u0131lan Alt\u0131n Mikrofon Yar\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131\u2019n\u0131n \xF6n elemelerinde aralar\u0131nda Zeki M\xFCren ve R\xFC\xE7han \xC7amay\u2019\u0131n da bulundu\u011Fu 46 ki\u015Filik \xF6n j\xFCri yar\u0131\u015Fman\u0131n finaline kalacak 7 grubu se\xE7erler. Finale sadece 5 grubun kalaca\u011F\u0131 a\xE7\u0131klansa da \xF6n elemelerden sonra finale 7 grup kal\u0131r. Erkin Koray ise \u201CBir Eyl\xFCl Ak\u015Fam\u0131\u201D par\xE7as\u0131 ile finale kalamadan elenir. 10 konserlik turneden sonra Siluetler grubu \u201CLorke Lorke\u201D par\xE7as\u0131 ile yar\u0131\u015Fmay\u0131 kazan\u0131r. Yar\u0131\u015Fman\u0131n di\u011Fer finalistleri ise \u201C\xC7ay\u0131r \xC7imen Geze Geze\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile Mavi I\u015F\u0131klar, \u201CBah\xE7elere Geldi Bahar\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile Sel\xE7uk Alag\xF6z, \u201CHer G\xFCn Kavga Var\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile Cahit Oben, \u201CY\xE2rim\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile Ali Atasagun D\xF6rtl\xFCs\xFC ve \u201CKaleden Top Atarlar\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile TPAO Batman Orkestras\u0131 olur. Yar\u0131\u015Fma sonunda H\xFCrriyet Gazetesi t\xFCm finalistlere plak \xE7\u0131kart\u0131r."
