  title: 'Erkin Koray - Meçhul (1968)',
  image: './posters/erkin-koray-mechul.jpg',
  info: /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("div", {
    className: "content-capsule",
    children: [/*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Erkin Koray, 1941\u2019de istanbul\u2019da do\u011Fdu. 1965 y\u0131l\u0131nda Almanya'n\u0131n Hamburg \u015Fehrine giden Erkin Koray 1966 y\u0131l\u0131nda T\xFCrkiye'ye d\xF6n\xFC\u015F\xFCnden sonra Erkin Koray D\xF6rtl\xFCs\xFC adl\u0131 grubu kurdu. 1967 y\u0131l\u0131nda bas\u0131lan, bir y\xFCz\xFCnde \"K\u0131zlar\u0131 da Al\u0131n Askere\", di\u011Fer y\xFCz\xFCnde \"A\u015Fk Oyunu\" adl\u0131 par\xE7alar bulunan 45'li\u011Fi ile \xF6nemli ba\u015Far\u0131 kazand\u0131. \xD6zellikle \"K\u0131zlar\u0131 da Al\u0131n Askere\" par\xE7as\u0131 Erkin Koray'\u0131n geni\u015F kitleler taraf\u0131ndan tan\u0131nmas\u0131nda \xF6nemli rol oynam\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r. 1968 y\u0131l\u0131nda, H\xFCrriyet Gazetesi taraf\u0131ndan yap\u0131lan \"Alt\u0131n Mikrofon\" yar\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131na kat\u0131ld\u0131. Bu yar\u0131\u015Fmada 4. olan Erkin Koray'\u0131n yar\u0131\u015Fmadaki \u015Fark\u0131lar\u0131 \"Me\xE7hul\" ve \"\xC7i\xE7ek Da\u011F\u0131\" daha sonra bir plak \u015Firketi taraf\u0131ndan piyasaya \xE7\u0131kar\u0131larak 800 bin adet gibi b\xFCy\xFCk tiraj yapt\u0131. Bu ilk \xF6nemli ba\u015Far\u0131y\u0131, 60'l\u0131 y\u0131llar\u0131n sonlar\u0131na dek ard\u0131 ard\u0131na gelen: \"Anma Arkada\u015F\", \"Hop Hop Gelsin\", \"Sana Bir \u015Eeyler Olmu\u015F\", \"Seni Her G\xF6rd\xFC\u011F\xFCmde\" gibi hepsi b\xFCy\xFCk be\u011Feni toplayan par\xE7alar takip etmi\u015Ftir."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 257,
      columnNumber: 49
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "1969 y\u0131l\u0131nda kurdu\u011Fu Yeralt\u0131 D\xF6rtl\xFCs\xFC adl\u0131 grubu ile T\xFCrkiye'de ilk \"Underground\" m\xFCzik ak\u0131m\u0131n\u0131n \xF6nc\xFCs\xFC oldu. 70'li y\u0131llar\u0131n ba\u015Flar\u0131na gelindi\u011Finde Koray T\xFCrkiye'de olduk\xE7a geni\u015F bir dinleyici kitlesine sahiptir ve kendine \xF6zg\xFC m\xFCzik \xE7izgisi belirginle\u015Fmi\u015F durumdad\u0131r."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 257,
      columnNumber: 977
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "1971'de Erkin Koray S\xFCper Grup, 1972'de Ter gruplar\u0131n\u0131 kuran Koray , 1970-1974 y\u0131llar\u0131 aras\u0131nda T\xFCrkiye m\xFCzik listelerinde \xFCst s\u0131ralarda yer alan klasikle\u015Fmi\u015F bir\xE7ok esere imza atm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r. \"\u0130lahi Morluk\", \"A\u015Fka \u0130nanm\u0131yorum\", \"Mesafeler\", \"Z\xFCleyha\", \"Silinmeyen Hat\u0131ralar\", 1974'te \"\u015Ea\u015Fk\u0131n\", \"Fesuphanallah\" bu d\xF6nem eserlerindendir."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 257,
      columnNumber: 1252
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Yenilik\xE7i, sentezci, deneyci bir m\xFCzik \xE7izgisi olan Erkin Koray; s\u0131ra d\u0131\u015F\u0131 \u015Fark\u0131 s\xF6zleri, kendine \xF6zg\xFC vokal bi\xE7emi, uzun sa\xE7lar\u0131, \xF6zg\xFCn k\u0131yafetleri ve bunun gibi daha bir\xE7ok nedenle d\xF6nemin yay\u0131n tekeli olan T\xFCrkiye Radyo Televizyon Kurumu TRT taraf\u0131ndan d\u0131\u015Flanm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r. Eserlerinin nerede ise tamam\u0131 yak\u0131n zamanlara kadar, TRT denetimi taraf\u0131ndan yay\u0131mlanmaya uygun g\xF6r\xFClmemi\u015Ftir. Bu durum T\xFCrkiye'de \xF6zel yay\u0131n kurulu\u015Flar\u0131n\u0131n ortaya \xE7\u0131k\u0131\u015F\u0131na kadar s\xFCregelmi\u015F ve Koray'\u0131n dinleyici kitlesinin s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 kalmas\u0131na yol a\xE7m\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r."
    }, void 0, false, {
