  info: /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("div", {
    className: "content-capsule",
    children: [/*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "TPAO Batman Orkestras\u0131 1963 y\u0131l\u0131nda kuruldu. Orkestra, TPAO'nun o g\xFCnlerde sanata yapt\u0131\u011F\u0131 yat\u0131r\u0131m\u0131n sonucuydu. Tek i\u015Fleri m\xFCzik olan bu insanlar TPAO g\xF6revlendirmesiyle kurumun \u015Fubelerinin oldu\u011Fu her yerde konserler vermeye ba\u015Flad\u0131lar. \u015E\xF6hretlerini ise 1968 y\u0131l\u0131nda kat\u0131ld\u0131klar\u0131 Alt\u0131n Mikrofon \u015Eark\u0131 Yar\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131'nda kazand\u0131klar\u0131 birincili\u011Fin ard\u0131ndan yakalad\u0131lar. H\xFCrriyet Gazetesi\u2019nin 1968 y\u0131l\u0131nda d\xFCzenledi\u011Fi Alt\u0131n Mikrofon \u015Eark\u0131 Yar\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131\u2019n\u0131n finalinde Haramiler, Erkin Koray ve Mo\u011Follar\u2019\u0131 \u201CMe\u015Felidir Engin de Da\u011Flar Me\u015Feli\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131yla ge\xE7en TPAO Batman Orkestras\u0131 o y\u0131lki yar\u0131\u015Fman\u0131n birincisi oldu."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 268,
      columnNumber: 49
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "1967- 1969 y\u0131llar\u0131 aras\u0131nda Anadolu ezgilerini popla bulu\u015Fturan orkestran\u0131n solisti \u0130lhan Telli, \u015Eeker Alal\u0131m \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 aranje eden isimdir. Anadolu Pop M\xFCzi\u011Fi\u2019nin \xF6nc\xFC isimlerinden biri olan Telli; Dario Moreno \xD6d\xFCl\xFC, Akdeniz Dostluk ve Bar\u0131\u015F M\xFCzik \xD6d\xFCl\xFC, Tanju Okan Ses Yar\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131 \xF6d\xFCllerini de kazanm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r."
