  title: 'Erol Büyükburç - Artık Sevmeyeceğim (1969)',
  image: './posters/erol-büyükbürc-artik-sevmeyecegim.jpg',
  info: /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("div", {
    className: "",
    children: [/*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Lise y\u0131llar\u0131nda kurdu\u011Fu m\xFCzik grubuyla amat\xF6r m\xFCzik \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmalar\u0131na ba\u015Flar. \u0130stanbul Belediye Konservatuar\u0131nda \u015Fan dersleri alan B\xFCy\xFCkbur\xE7 18 ya\u015F\u0131nda \u0130smet S\u0131ral Orkestras\u0131 e\u015Fli\u011Finde Caddebostan Maksim Gazinosunda solist olarak ilk sahne \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131n\u0131 yapar, \u201CJezabel\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131 ile ad\u0131n\u0131 duyurmaya ba\u015Flar."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 317,
      columnNumber: 34
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Askerli\u011Fini Urfa Orduevi\u2019nde yapan B\xFCy\xFCkbur\xE7, bu s\u0131rada \u015Fark\u0131 s\xF6ylerken Leyla Sayar\u2019la tan\u0131\u015F\u0131r ve askerlik d\xF6n\xFC\u015F\xFC Sayar\u2019\u0131n deste\u011Fiyle \u0130stanbul\u2019un \xF6nemli kul\xFCplerinde ismini duyurmaya ba\u015Flar. Kendi ad\u0131na kurdu\u011Fu ilk orkestras\u0131 \u201CErol B\xFCy\xFCkbur\xE7 Vokal Grubu\u201D ile Four Lads, Platters tarz\u0131 vokal m\xFCzi\u011Finin ve doo-wop\u2019\u0131n T\xFCrkiye\u2019deki \xF6nc\xFC uygulay\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 olur."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 317,
      columnNumber: 341
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Profesyonel ilk m\xFCzik \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131 1961'de \xE7\u0131kan \u2018\u2018Little Lucy\"dir. Balkan Festivali'nde \u2018\u2018En \u0130yi \u015Eark\u0131c\u0131\u2019\u2019 \xF6d\xFCl\xFCn\xFC al\u0131r, uzun y\u0131llar Efsaneler Orkestras\u0131 ile \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r. 62 y\u0131l\u0131ndan itibaren \u015Eerif Y\xFCzba\u015F\u0131o\u011Flu Orkestras\u0131yla l\xFCks mek\xE2nlarda sahne alan sanat\xE7\u0131, bir sene Bo\u011Fazi\xE7i M\xFCzik Festivali\u2019nde \u201CEn iyi \u015Eark\u0131c\u0131\u201D ve \u201CEn \u0130yi \u015Eark\u0131\u201D \xF6d\xFCllerini kazan\u0131r ve bu yar\u0131\u015Fmada \u015Eerif Y\xFCzba\u015F\u0131o\u011Flu Orkestras\u0131 e\u015Fli\u011Finde \u201CAdieu Mon Pays\u201D \u015Fark\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 seslendirir. Sanat\xE7\u0131 1964'de bu orkestradan ayr\u0131larak Necdet Karar, \xC7arli ve C\xFCret I\u015F\u0131\xF6zl\xFC\u2019n\xFCn bulundu\u011Fu kadro ile bir grup kurar."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 317,
      columnNumber: 699
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "Erol B\xFCy\xFCkbur\xE7, 1968 y\u0131l\u0131nda \u201CAlt\u0131n \u015Eark\u0131lar\u201D, 1969 y\u0131l\u0131nda ise \u201CYasemin\u201D plaklar\u0131n\u0131 yapar. \u201CK\u0131r\u0131k Kalp\u201D, \u201CYasemin\u201D, \u201CG\xF6zlerime \u0130yice Bak\u201D, \u201CGel Gir Koluma\u201D gibi pop\xFCler m\xFCzi\u011Fimizin ilk hit \u015Fark\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 \xDCmit Ero\u011Flu d\xFCzenlemeleri ile hayata ge\xE7irir. 1969 y\u0131l\u0131nda \u201CSerseri / Art\u0131k Sevmeyece\u011Fim\u201D pla\u011F\u0131n\u0131 \xE7\u0131kar\u0131r. Bu plaktaki \u201CArt\u0131k Sevmeyece\u011Fim\u201D par\xE7as\u0131n\u0131n s\xF6zleri ve m\xFCzi\u011Fi Suat Say\u0131n\u2019a aittir."
    }, void 0, false, {
      fileName: _jsxFileName,
      lineNumber: 317,
      columnNumber: 1264
    }, this), /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("p", {
      children: "K\u0131yafet ve tav\u0131rlar\u0131yla \u201CT\xFCrkiye\u2019nin Elvis Presley\u2019i\u201D olarak tan\u0131nan B\xFCy\xFCkbur\xE7, pek \xE7ok ilke de imza atar. Bu ilkler aras\u0131nda olan ilk T\xFCrk pop m\xFCzi\u011Fi bestecisi, ilk t\xFCrk\xFC d\xFCzenlemecisi, ilk turneye \xE7\u0131kan pop\xE7u gibi \xF6zellikleri sanat hayat\u0131nda bir araya getirir. Sanat\xE7\u0131 yar\u0131m y\xFCzy\u0131la yak\u0131n bir sanat ya\u015Fam\u0131na 8 ta\u015F plak, 65 tane 45\u2019lik, 20 fotoroman, 5 long-play, 1800\u2019e yak\u0131n beste, 30\u2019a yak\u0131n film ve 200\u2019e yak\u0131n \xF6d\xFCl\xFC s\u0131\u011Fd\u0131rmay\u0131 ba\u015Far\u0131r."
    }, void 0, false, {
